Here are the following workarounds that restored the PHP outline

Remove "<" character
{code:php}
<?php

function test_func() {
	$x = 'a' . 'b';
}

?>
{code}

Remove closing PHP tag
{code:php}
<?php

function test_func() {
	$x = '<a' . 'b';
}
{code}

Separating "<" character and a-z character

